body:
Yesterday I was on Kohi Practice 2, fighting people casually, until I was asked randomly to 1v1 by Bensco for YT, I accepted and we went on to have lots of great, close fights. I was not able to record, as I was lagging way more than usual when recording.  

Video: https://youtube.com/watch?v=msXiR6Mj6RA 
             https://youtube.com/watch?v=msXiR6Mj6RA 
             https://youtube.com/watch?v=msXiR6Mj6RA 

Great PvPer. Gfs!
